Description: Czechoslovak ABO format parsing library for PHP
 This library provides a parser for Czechoslovak ABO (Account Bank Output)
 format files, which are commonly used for bank statement processing in
 Czech Republic and Slovakia.
 .
 The library includes:
  - AboParser class for parsing ABO files
  - Support for 074 and 075 record types
  - Proper character encoding handling for Czech/Slovak text
  - Command-line tools for ABO to JSON conversion
  - Full PSR-4 autoloading support
